{"id": "art-1401", "label": "Art. 1401", "title": "Art. 1401", "slug": "art-1401", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_300528140\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2229\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_300528140\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 140<sup>1</sup></span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1445107930\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2228\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1445107930\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Consiliul de <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>\nalege dintre membrii s&#259;i un <span class=SpellE>pre&#351;edinte</span> al\nconsiliului. Prin actul constitutiv se poate stipula c&#259; <span\nclass=SpellE>pre&#351;edintele</span> consiliului este numit de adunarea\ngeneral&#259; ordinar&#259;, care <span class=SpellE>nume&#351;te</span>\nconsiliul.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1607673869\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2227\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1607673869\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)<span class=SpellE>Pre&#351;edintele</span> este numit\npentru o durat&#259; care nu poate <span class=SpellE>dep&#259;&#351;i</span>\ndurata mandatului s&#259;u de administrator.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1051155791\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2226\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1051155791\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)<span class=SpellE>Pre&#351;edintele</span> poate fi\nrevocat oricând de c&#259;tre consiliul de <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>.\nDac&#259; <span class=SpellE>pre&#351;edintele</span> a fost numit de adunarea\ngeneral&#259;, va putea fi revocat numai de aceasta.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_724272812\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2225\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_724272812\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)<span class=SpellE>Pre&#351;edintele</span>\ncoordoneaz&#259; activitatea consiliului <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nraporteaz&#259; cu privire la aceasta adun&#259;rii generale a <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarilor</span>. El vegheaz&#259; la buna <span\nclass=SpellE>func&#355;ionare</span> a organelor <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_815792548\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2224\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_815792548\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)În cazul în care <span class=SpellE>pre&#351;edintele</span>\nse afl&#259; în imposibilitate temporar&#259; de a-<span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nexercita <span class=SpellE>atribu&#355;iile</span>, pe durata st&#259;rii\nrespective de imposibilitate consiliul de <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>\npoate îns&#259;rcina pe un alt administrator cu îndeplinirea <span\nclass=SpellE>func&#355;iei</span> de <span class=SpellE>pre&#351;edinte</span>.</span></p>"}